{
  "stem": "1799.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It would be better for all of us, something to that effect.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I did volunteer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's when I came to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't know what to believe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did learn, over the years that I was in camp, that a change of camp or a change of activity somehow kept me going.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was something in this constant change of scenery and adaptation to new conditions ended up being good.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I looked for that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so, I grabbed the chance to volunteer and go to Dachau with the group of-- how big was the transport?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't that large.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was 300, 400 people on a train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How did you-- so you got there by train?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Dachau.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was a pretty long ride.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was two nights.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a long train ride.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] in the first camp, it was actually Kaufering.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "K-A-U-F-E-R-I-N-G.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In that first camp, conditions were pretty awful.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You could see that people were being mistreated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "People were being forced to work in substandard conditions, with less than normal food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Kaufering, by the way, has, oh, maybe eight, ten different camps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a large sub-camp of Dachau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this was just one of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Typical day was at daybreak, there was what they called appell, which means that you had to rally and stand outside, regardless of the weather, and be-- wait for your name to be called.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and then you soon after, would rally to go to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would always first have a call of, of rally to mention the names.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then the kommandos would go out to work at the various groups.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, kommandos, so that's what the Germans called it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were contingents of work groups.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
